{
  "id": "adv_bond_ngs_01_01",
  "title": "伊吹渚1",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_01-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "やっほー！　渚ちゃーん、琴乃ちゃーん！\nお昼ご飯一緒に食べよー！　芽衣、お弁当持って来た！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yahooー! Nagisa-chanー‚ Kotono-chanー!\nLunch‚ let's eat togetherー! Mei‚ brought lunch box!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 4.666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 10.2541269938
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_01-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "今日は琴乃ちゃんお仕事でお休みなんだよね\nせっかく来てくれたし、私の教室で食べよっか！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono-chan has the day off for work today\nSince you've come all the way here‚ let's eat in my classroom!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.2541269938,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.6409524281
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_01-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "はーい！　失礼しまーす！\nもう芽衣お腹ペコペコだよ～。いただきまーす！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yesー! Excuse meー!\nMei is really being hungry~. Let's eatー!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.6409524281,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 30.1754871368
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_01-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "もぐもぐ……。あ、芽衣、今日大ニュースがあるんだ\nさっきの数学の授業中にね、すっごい夢見たの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Munch munch…. Ah‚ Mei‚ has big news today\nJust now‚ during math class‚ I had an amazing dream!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.1754871368,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 42.380636247
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_01-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "夢……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A dream…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.380636247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.051792717
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_01-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣がペンを回すとドーナツが空から落ちてくる夢！\n沢山回したから沢山降ってきて……食べたかったな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A dream where when Mei turns pen‚ donuts fall from the sky!\nTurned it around a lot and came down a lot… wanted to eat some~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.051792717,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 56.4011122386
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_01-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "とっても楽しそうだけど……授業中に寝てたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It sounds like a lot of fun… but‚ did you sleep during class?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.4011122386,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 61.1485044797
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_01-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっとだけだから、へーきへーき！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's only for a moment‚ no problemー no problemー!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.1485044797,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.3741053105
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_01-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "もー、寝ちゃダメだよ\n最近お疲れなのは分かるけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Seriously‚ you shouldn't sleep\nI know you’ve been tired lately…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.3741053105,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.8074158192
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_01-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "だって黒板に書いてある文字が呪文みたいなんだもん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because the words written on blackboard are like a spell word",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.8074158192,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_01-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "あはは……まあ、分からなくもないかな\n数式とか、いろんな記号使うもんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahaha… Well‚ it’s not that I don’t understand\nBecause‚ it uses formulas and various symbols",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.7748987358,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 83.2787308534
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_01-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "でしょでしょ！　ほんとに呪文だったらいいのになー\nドーナツが出てくる呪文とか！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ yes! I really hope that's spell wordー\nA spell that makes donuts appear!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.2787308534,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 90.7323363463
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_01-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、それはもはや魔法の授業だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haha‚ that's magic class now",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.7323363463,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 94.7082093239
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_01-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "ドーナツの話してたら、お腹減ってきちゃった\nドーナツ食べたいなぁ～……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Talking about donuts‚ makes me hungry\nI want to eat a donut~…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.7082093239,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.7077557564
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_01-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "今お弁当食べてるところだよね！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're eating your lunch right now!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.7077557564,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 104.9030367692
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_01-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "ドーナツは別腹だよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have room for donut!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.9030367692,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 107.425308903
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_01-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "あ、それなら――\nそんな芽衣ちゃんには、魔法をかけてあげましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ then――\nLet's cast a magic on Mei-chan",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.425308903,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.0660810868
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_01-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "ええっ！？　魔法！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What!? Magic!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.0660810868,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 116.1303668658
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_01-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "なぎなぎマジカル～くるくるぽん！　はい、どうぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nagi-nagi magical~ kuru-kuru pon! Here you are",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.1303668658,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 121.0551033496
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_01-mei011.m4a",
      "text": "わ！　渚ちゃんのバッグからドーナツが出てきた！\nもらっていいの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow! A donut appeared in Nagisa's bag!\nCan I have it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.0551033496,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 127.5986861069
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_01-ngs010.m4a",
      "text": "うん、いいよ\nおやつに食べようと思って持って来てたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ it's okay\nI brought it to eat as a snack",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.5986861069,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 132.0762369791
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_01-mei012.m4a",
      "text": "わーい、ありがとう！\n……あ！　それならお返しに芽衣も魔法かけてあげる！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wowー‚ thank you!\n…Ah! Then‚ I'll cast a magic on you in return!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.0762369791,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 139.3270303407
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_01-mei013.m4a",
